column1:
Please use this sheet to rate your favorite (and not-so-favorite) lunch spots.
If you have an opinion of a restaurant, please rate it on a scale from 1 (worst) to 5 (best)
If you've never been to a restaurant, or don't have an opinion about it, please leave that item blank.
Feel free to rate as many or as few restaurants as you like.  If something isn't on the list, add it!
Add your name and slack handle to a new column and get to rating!
